data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 2 full bath rambler in fantastic location. Home boasts an open floor plan with Heat Pump & Central air conditioning. Upgraded aluminum duct work, interior & exterior paint, new stove & microwave. Fully fenced backyard with newer landscaping, fruit trees, fish pond and a concrete slab for the gazebo is ideal for entertaining. Close to library, schools, shopping & bus lines.
